file.name: swagger.yaml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0.0"
info:
    title: Football Api League
    description: Example of how implement a complete restfull lifeCycle
    termsOfService: http://example.com/terms/
    contact:
      name: API Team
      url: https://mojitoverdeintw.blogspot.com
      email: ldipotet.job@gmail.com
    license:
      name: MIT
      url: https://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0.html
    version: 1.0.0
servers:
  - url: http://localhost:9000/apirest
paths:
    /football/matchs:
      get:
        summary: "Return all fotball matchs from the beginning"
        operationId: "getMatchGame"
        tags:
          - "football"
        responses:
          '200':
            description: "successful operation"
            content:
              application/json:
                schema:
                  $ref: "#/components/schemas/Matchs"
            schema:
            type: "array"
            items:
              $ref: "#/definitions/football"
          '400':
            description: "Bad Request"
          '403':
            description: "Forbidden"
          '406':
            description: "Not Acceptable Status Value"
          '500':
            description: "Internal Server Error"

components:
  schemas:
    Matchs:
      type: array
      items:
        $ref: "#/components/schemas/Match"
    Match:
      type: object
      properties:
        hometeam:
          $ref: "#/components/schemas/TemplateTeam"
        awayteam:
          $ref: "#/components/schemas/TemplateTeam"
        date:
          type: string
          format: date-time
        season:
          type: string
    TemplateTeam:
      type: object
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
        goals:
          type: integer
          format: int32
        goalsPlayer:
          $ref: "#/components/schemas/GoalsPlayer"
    GoalsPlayer:
      type: object
      additionalProperties:
        $ref: "#/components/schemas/Minutes_Goals"
    Minutes_Goals:
      type: array
      items:
        type: string
